mods.abstract: A black and white negative taped to and framed by a masking sheet advertising the Faron Young Show featuring the Plainsmen Quartet, Jamey Ryan, the Deputies, and Pete Street. The portion of the negative that would have featured information on the talent agency has been cut out and is missing. The negative would have been used to create a corresponding printing plate.
